Odaily Planet Daily News According to Spot On Chain monitoring, 8 hours ago, the whale address "0x257" deposited 4 assets worth US$7.96 million to Binance, including 3 major DeFi tokens, specifically: 
13,816 AAVE, +2.56 million US dollars in profit (+255%); 
161,463 LINK, +2.13 million US dollars in profit (+213%); 
85,529 UNI, +258,000 US dollars in profit (+52%); 
289,399 EIGEN (US$531,000). 
The whale has been a long-term holder of AAVE, LINK and UNI since mid-2022.
